=head1 DESCRIPTION

The object that you configure to copy snapshots from one namespace to a
namespace in another Amazon Web Services Region.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 DestinationKmsKeyId => Str

The ID of the KMS key to use to encrypt your snapshots in the
destination Amazon Web Services Region.


=head2 DestinationRegion => Str

The destination Amazon Web Services Region to copy snapshots to.


=head2 NamespaceName => Str

The name of the namespace to copy snapshots from in the source Amazon
Web Services Region.


=head2 SnapshotCopyConfigurationArn => Str

The ARN of the snapshot copy configuration object.


=head2 SnapshotCopyConfigurationId => Str

The ID of the snapshot copy configuration object.


=head2 SnapshotRetentionPeriod => Int

The retention period of snapshots that are copied to the destination
Amazon Web Services Region.



